{"word":"G3768 - οὔπω - oúpō - oo'-po - Hitherto not","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οὔπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">oúpō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">oo'-po</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hitherto not</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இன்னும், இப்பொழுதும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"not yet"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3756 - οὐ - ou - oo/3756\">G3756</a> and <a href=\"#/G4452 - -πω - -pō - po/4452\">G4452</a>; <i>not yet:</i> - hitherto not, (no . . .) as yet, not yet.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}